dmca.title: Copyrights Infringe Notice - garagemoney.net
dmca.body:
-----Original Message-----
From: TemplateBlowout [mailto:sk@templateblowout.com] 
Sent: Sunday, September 12, 2004 3:45 PM
To: copyright@theplanet.com; abuse@theplanet.com
Subject: Copyrights Infringe Notice - garagemoney.net



Whomsoever It May Concern

It has come to our attention, a website hosted with you, 
garagemoney.net, is illegally selling our copyrighted content.

Exact Location of copyrights infringe content:
http://www.garagemoney.net

I request you to please take necessary action to stop them from 
allowing their visitors, access to our files.

Email Attachment contains:

1) DCMA Notice.
2) U.S Copyrights filing copy.
3) Protected Content.

Should you require any further information, you can reach me at: 
sk@templateblowout.com and via phone: +91-98851-03405

Your prompt attention in this matter will be appriciated.
Thank you in advance.

Best Regards,
SK.
XecureNet, Inc.
